Package com.nomicflux.wuwei

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ST<S,A>
    MonadRec which allows for actions within a limited scope, to be chained together with monadic or applicative actions and ended with ST.runST().
    STRef<S,A>
    A class to work with mutable references within the ST monad
    STRef.STRefCreator<S,A>
    Used to create an STRef within an ST monad.
    STRefModifier<A>
    Utility class for creating composable units of work on STRefs.
    World<S>
    A phantom type.
